data.description: Immaculate 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath, 3755 sq. ft. home in sought after Meadow Glen! New LVP flooring throughout the main level is the perfect compliment to the open floor plan, ideal for entertaining. Dual staircase provides upper level access from the front entrance and kitchen. Dreamed of having your own wine tasting room? Home office? This home has it all! The family room features a gas fireplace, eat-in breakfast area & tons of natural light. Open kitchen with an abundance of cabinets, granite countertops, island, updated appliances & new tile backsplash. New carpet on upper level!  Oversized primary suite with sitting area, en suite with dual vanity & massive walk-in closet. 2nd and 3rd bedrooms share jack and jill bath. 4th bedroom has a private full bath as well. Large 5th bedroom/bonus room/theater room, you decide! Fresh paint throughout. New roof 2017. Granite tile patio. Backs up to large HOA maintained common area.
